keywords enchant
---
Syntax: enchant show
        enchant buy <enchantment>

Allows players to permanently enchant wearable items using a spell matrix and
enchantment objects. Place a wearable item and one or more enchantment items
in your inventory, then use 'enchant show' to see available options or
'enchant buy <enchantment>' to apply an enchantment for quest points.
